[Mark: I miss you so much suddenly.]

18
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:51,940
[Kit: You're so dramatic.]

19
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:55,020
You should go back and accompany Mark.

20
00:00:56,620 --> 00:00:59,500
You come to accompany me
after school every time.

21
