23
00:01:16,900 --> 00:01:18,660
We need to spend some time
with the people we love.

24
00:01:19,900 --> 00:01:21,100
Sometimes,

25
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:24,100
the most meaningful moments

26
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:26,539
might not be the most important moments.

27
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:30,620
Instead, they are the ordinary days

28
00:01:30,620 --> 00:01:32,380
