29
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:33,539
Kit.

30
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:35,100
Be my partner.

31
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:45,820
Hey.

32
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:47,340
