36
00:03:54,690 --> 00:03:55,500
Wayu.

37
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:09,530
Remember, when you draw the bow,

38
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:11,580
you need to draw it slowly.

39
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:14,820
Place your hand under your chin.

40
00:04:16,769 --> 00:04:18,220
Pull the bowstring towards your nose.

41
00:04:24,900 --> 00:04:26,020
Are you still angry at me?

42
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:37,450
Actually,

43
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:40,580
I should be the one asking that question.

44
00:04:42,570 --> 00:04:44,020
I'm sorry, P'Thanu.

45
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:47,460
Even though

46
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:49,140
you had told me everything

47
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:51,540
and explained yourself to me,

48
00:04:55,020 --> 00:04:57,100
I still didn't believe in you.

49
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,900
