that are out of our control

56
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:55,020
and fail to hit the target.

57
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,260
Wayu, it's fine.

58
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,700
Let's try again.

59
00:06:12,890 --> 00:06:14,130
If you hit the target this time,

60
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,220
let's begin a new relationship.

61
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,900
Try and get the feel.

62
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:33,100
Are you ready?

63
00:06:34,340 --> 00:06:34,980
I am.

64
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,570
Let's begin a new relationship.

65
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:19,340
Okay, P'Thanu.

66
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,780
If you want to know why I was hurt,

67
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:22,660
you can ask Tongtrai yourself.

68
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:45,740
I'll leave first.

69
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:15,860
Wa!

70
