74
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,700
Two years old.

75
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:23,410
Hmm.

76
00:09:23,410 --> 00:09:25,420
Two years old, huh?

77
00:09:25,420 --> 00:09:26,620
Hmm?

78
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:28,820
Why are you here?

79
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:32,340
This.

80
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,460
You forgot your wallet.

81
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:34,820
That's why I brought it here for you.

82
00:09:35,340 --> 00:09:37,700
I was planning to take it and visit Pa
after this.

83
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:38,970
Thanks.

84
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:43,620
P'Kit,

85
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,970
